data.description: Charming 3 bed 2.5 bath home near the hospital, OIT Campus and in the hot springs neighborhood! Enjoy neighborhood walks or rides while you head to one of the several nearby parks or playgrounds! This home has a neat lot and location in that the garage is accessible from Peach street, while the front of the home borders Eldorado. The corner lot adds some room for the yard, activities and entertaining. 2 full bathrooms are located on the same level as the bedrooms and the kitchen is open to the eat in nook or dining room. Come see today if this property is right for you!
